vice", "checkoutservice", "emailservice", "frontend", "productcatalogservice", "redis", "shippingservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-01", "aiops-k8s-03", "aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-06", "aiops-k8s-08"]}, "status_combinations": "node_name,service_name,parent_pod,child_pod,operation_name,status_code,status_message,occurrence_count\naiops-k8s-03,frontend,frontend-0,frontend-0,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,2,,出现次数:1081\naiops-k8s-07,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,2,,出现次数:923\naiops-k8s-04,frontend,frontend-2,frontend-2,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,2,,出现次数:921\naiops-k8s-03,frontend,N/A,frontend-0,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,2,,出现次数:26\naiops-k8s-04,frontend,N/A,frontend-2,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,2,,出现次数:25\naiops-k8s-07,frontend,N/A,frontend-1,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,2,,出现次数:21\n", "matched_anomaly": "A fault occurred from 2025-06-12T11:02:54Z to 2025-06-12T11:17:54Z. Please identify the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-12 11:02:54+00:00 to 2025-06-12 11:17:54+00:00"}, "trace_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"failed to get ads\",\n    \"rpc error\",\n    \"code = Unknown desc\",\n    \"failed to retrieve ads\",\n    \"Exception in thread\",\n    \"java.lang.Error\",\n    \"Injected error\",\n    \"AdService-getRandomAds-exception-1749726175\",\n    \"caught ThrowException\",\n    \"Rule.execute\",\n    \"java.lang.Exception\",\n    \"Byteman agent\",\n    \"Agent failed to start\",\n    \"java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException\",\n    \"org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"AdService is throwing exceptions and failing to retrieve ads, possibly due to injected errors or Byteman agent issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Exception in thread \\\"grpc-default-executor-25897\\\" java.lang.Error: Injected error\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Frontend services are failing to retrieve ads from AdService, leading to rpc errors.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = Unknown desc = \\\"\\\"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Byteman agent issues causing repeated failures in AdService.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Agent failed to start! and java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的调用链数据，我已完成初步扫描分析。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CartService调用Redis的HGET操作从正常1.74ms激增至53.0ms（延迟倍数30.4倍），GetCart操作从2.59ms增至20.6ms（7.9倍），EmptyCart操作从2.31ms增至62.8ms（27.2倍）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis的HGET操作响应时间异常增长，表明Redis服务存在性能问题，影响了依赖它的cartservice\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CheckoutService的PlaceOrder操作从正常145.5ms降至45.3ms，但异常频次低，可能受到下游服务影响\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"ProductCatalogService的GetProduct操作从10.3ms增至20.7ms（2.0倍），存在轻微延迟\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 关键发现：\n\n1. **最显著的延迟异常**：cartservice与Redis之间的调用链显示严重延迟，特别是HGET操作延迟增长30倍，EmptyCart操作增长27倍。\n\n2. **根因分析**：\n   - **Redis是潜在根因**：Redis的HGET操作延迟异常，导致cartservice调用Redis时出现严重延迟\n   - **cartservice是受害者**：由于Redis性能问题，cartservice的多个操作都受到影响\n\n3. **调用链影响**：\n   - checkoutservice → cartservice → redis 这条调用链存在明显的延迟传播\n   - frontend → checkoutservice 的延迟相对较小，表明问题主要在下游服务\n\n4. **状态码分析**：所有状态码均为2（成功），但存在严重的性能延迟问题。\n\n需要进一步分析Redis的具体性能指标来确认根因。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的异常指标数据，我现在进行初始扫描分析。从数据中发现了多个显著的异常模式。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"node_cpu_usage_rate\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"cpu_usage\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点内存严重不足，node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes下降71.74%，node_memory_usage_rate上升35.7%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes从14.77GB降至6.97GB，node_memory_usage_rate从53.22%升至76.35%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-01\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点内存使用率异常升高，node_memory_usage_rate上升55.96%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate从38.38%升至68.2%，node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes从10.58GB降至5.58GB\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点内存使用率显著上升，node_memory_usage_rate上升58.9%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate从29.73%升至54.55%，node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes从11.49GB降至7.31GB\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-03\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点CPU使用率异常升高，node_cpu_usage_rate上升41.63%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_cpu_usage_rate从32.58%升至49.71%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"服务响应时间异常波动，rrt_max下降60.92%，rrt下降16.5%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max从7372.5ms降至3930.0ms，rrt从904.96ms降至767.01ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"前端服务最大响应时间异常，rrt_max下降17.06%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max从194824.5ms降至164200.0ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"购物车服务最大响应时间异常升高，rrt_max上升33.18%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max从7696.0ms升至10757.0ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-pd\",\n      \"reason\": \"TiDB PD组件CPU使用率异常下降，cpu_usage下降42.36%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cpu_usage从0.62降至0.4\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
